            <title>[LUCENE-248] [PATCH] Add StopFilter ignoreCase option</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-248</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Wanted to have the ability to ignore case in the stop filter.  In some cases, I&lt;br/&gt;
don&apos;t want to have to lower case before passing through the stop filter, b/c I&lt;br/&gt;
may need case preserved for other analysis further down the stream, yet I don&apos;t&lt;br/&gt;
need the stopwords and I don&apos;t want to have to apply stopword filters twice.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Operating System: other&lt;br/&gt;
